sequenceDiagram
    participant Host as 👤 Host
    participant P2 as 👤 Player 2
    participant UI as ⚛️ Web App
    participant GameAPI as 🎮 Game API
    participant WS as 🔌 WebSocket
    participant DB as 🗄️ Database
    
    Note over Host,DB: Game Creation and Start Flow
    
    Host->>UI: Click "Create Game"
    UI->>Host: Show game creation form
    
    Host->>UI: Enter game name<br/>Set max players (8)<br/>Set privacy (public)
    Host->>UI: Click "Create"
    
    UI->>GameAPI: POST /games<br/>{name, hostId, settings}
    
    GameAPI->>DB: Create game record<br/>(status: lobby)
    GameAPI->>DB: Add host as first player
    DB-->>GameAPI: Game created {gameId}
    
    GameAPI->>WS: Subscribe host to game channel
    GameAPI-->>UI: 201 Created {game}
    
    UI->>Host: Navigate to game lobby<br/>Show game code for sharing
    
    Note over Host,DB: Other players join
    
    P2->>UI: Browse games or enter code
    UI->>GameAPI: GET /games (list available)
    GameAPI->>DB: Query open games
    DB-->>GameAPI: Game list
    GameAPI-->>UI: 200 OK {games}
    
    P2->>UI: Click "Join Game"
    UI->>GameAPI: POST /games/{id}/players<br/>{playerId, playerName}
    
    GameAPI->>DB: Validate game not full
    GameAPI->>DB: Add player to game
    DB-->>GameAPI: Player added
    
    GameAPI->>WS: Publish player.joined event
    GameAPI-->>UI: 200 OK {game}
    
    WS-->>UI: player.joined event
    UI->>Host: Show "Player 2 joined"
    UI->>P2: Show lobby with all players
    
    Note over Host,P2: Players mark ready
    
    P2->>UI: Click "Ready"
    UI->>GameAPI: PATCH /games/{id}/players/{playerId}<br/>{isReady: true}
    
    GameAPI->>DB: Update player ready status
    GameAPI->>WS: Publish player.ready.changed event
    WS-->>UI: Update ready indicators
    
    Note over Host,DB: Host starts game when ready
    
    Host->>UI: Click "Start Game"<br/>(requires 2+ players)
    
    UI->>GameAPI: POST /games/{id}/start
    
    GameAPI->>DB: Validate 2+ players
    
    alt Less than 2 players
        GameAPI-->>UI: 400 Bad Request<br/>"Need at least 2 players"
        UI->>Host: Show error message
    else 2+ players ready
        GameAPI->>DB: Update game status<br/>(status: starting)
        
        GameAPI->>GameAPI: Initialize deck<br/>(52 cards, shuffled)
        
        GameAPI->>GameAPI: Deal starting hands<br/>(7 cards each)
        
        GameAPI->>GameAPI: Place first card<br/>on discard pile
        
        GameAPI->>GameAPI: Determine starting player<br/>(random or host)
        
        GameAPI->>DB: Update game state<br/>(status: in_progress)
        DB-->>GameAPI: Game started
        
        GameAPI->>WS: Publish game.started event<br/>{startingPlayerId, initialState}
        
        GameAPI-->>UI: 200 OK {game}
        
        WS-->>UI: game.started event
        
        UI->>Host: Navigate to game board<br/>Show hand and game state
        UI->>P2: Navigate to game board<br/>Show hand and game state
        
        WS-->>UI: turn.changed event<br/>{currentPlayerId}
        
        UI->>UI: Highlight current player
        UI->>UI: Enable actions for current player
        
        Note over Host,P2: Game is now in progress!
    end